262
00:23:55,486 --> 00:23:57,848
300 thousand pounds.

263
00:23:58,835 --> 00:24:01,155
Approximately.

264
00:24:41,587 --> 00:24:43,187
Bastard!

265
00:25:35,864 --> 00:25:37,747
- Matthew?
- Yeah?

266
00:25:37,909 --> 00:25:40,227
You know that plant...

267
00:25:40,343 --> 00:25:42,836
