Ounce for ounce, the really good
stuff is worth more than gold.

272
00:26:00,784 --> 00:26:03,320
Greenhouse, now!

273
00:26:05,264 --> 00:26:08,409
Here's what I think: we take
cuttings from the mother plant...

274
00:26:08,570 --> 00:26:12,105
